            </div>
            <div class="span2" style="text-align: right;">
                <a href="/2008/feb/04/quick-request/#comments">2 comments</a> |
                <a rel="bookmark" href="/2008/feb/04/quick-request/" title="Permanent link to this entry">&#x2732;</a>
