<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/dec/11/">&#x27a0;</a> December 11, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="apparently-america-over-whole-" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://baratunde.com/blog/archives/2007/12/apparently_america_is_over_the_whole_race_thing.html">Apparently, America is over the whole race thing. at goodCRIMETHINK</a></h4>

        
            
        

